RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT MSG_TYPE,DESCRIPTION FROM OLTM_MSG_TYPE ORDER BY MSG_TYPE
SELECT MEDIA,DESCRIPTION FROM MSTM_MEDIA WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A' ORDER BY MEDIA
SELECT BRANCH_CODE,BRANCH_NAME FROM OLTM_BRANCH WHERE AUTH_STAT='A' AND RECORD_STAT='O' ORDER BY BRANCH_CODE
SELECT MSG_TYPE,DESCRIPTION FROM OLTM_MSG_TYPE ORDER BY MSG_TYPE
SELECT DISTINCT NODE FROM MSTMS_MCS WHERE AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY NODE
SELECT MODULE_ID,MODULE_DESC FROM SMTB_MODULES WHERE RECORD_STAT='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A' ORDER BY MODULE_ID

SELECT A.ENTITY, B.ENTITY_NAME FROM LBTBS_BORROWER_ENTITIES A, OLTMS_CUSTOMER_ENTITY_DETAILS B WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND A.CUSTOMER_NO = ? AND A.VERSION_NO = (SELECT MAX(VERSION_NO) FROM LBTBS_BORROWER_ENTITIES WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND CUSTOMER_NO = ?) AND A.ENTITY = B.ENTITY AND A.CUSTOMER_NO = B.CUSTOMER_NO AND ? IN ('FC','LB') UNION SELECT A.ENTITY, B.ENTITY_NAME FROM LPTMS_PARTICIPANT_ENTITIES A, OLTMS_CUSTOMER_ENTITY_DETAILS B WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND A.CUSTOMER_NO = ? AND A.VERSION_NO = (SELECT MAX(VERSION_NO) FROM LPTMS_PARTICIPANT_ENTITIES WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND CUSTOMER_NO = ?) AND A.ENTITY = B.ENTITY AND A.CUSTOMER_NO = B.CUSTOMER_NO AND ? = 'LP' UNION SELECT '$$$', 'NO ENTITY' FROM DUAL
